      "unit_name": "Financial Statements of Sole Proprietorship",
      "chapter_name": "Financial Statements of Sole Proprietorship",
      "details": "Comprehensive project of any sole proprietorship business. This may start with journal entries and their ledgering, preparation of Trial balance, Trading and Profit and Loss Account and Balance Sheet. Expenses, incomes and profit (loss), assets and liabilities are to be depicted using pie chart / bar diagram. This may include simple GST related transactions."
