      "title": "Project Work: Financial Statement Analysis",
      "unit_name": "Analysis of Financial Statements",
      "chapter_name": "Analysis of Financial Statements",
      "details": "One specific project based on financial statement analysis of a company covering any two aspects from the following: 1. Comparative and common size financial statements, 2. Accounting Ratios, 3. Segment Reports, 4. Cash Flow Statements."
